      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 power plant. This unit features a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventive maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis weak points. Suspension geometry is tightened with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the MacPherson/multi-link setup provides maximum lateral grip. Minor aesthetic wear is present, but the drivetrain and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A visceral, analog driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
